plot: While the team is in Spain, McG makes a connection that leads the group to discover a potential threat stateside. Meanwhile, Noah and Hannah venture out of the office to get some information of their own.

When the team is on the ground in Spain, McG (Noah Mills) makes a connection, personal and professional, that leads the group to discover a potential threat stateside. Before they can act on that information, they need to stop assassins who are intent on killing their informant. Meanwhile, Noah (Tate Ellington) and Hannah (Sofia Pernas) both leave the office, following their own leads, to gather more information on their own.
